  "paras": [
    {
      "n": "¶ 1",
      "text": "In the hills above the old town stood a monastery whose gates had not opened to outsiders in decades. Its <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abbot\" data-syno=\"prior, monastery-head\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"math ka pradhan/mukhiya\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abbot ka matlab hai math ka pradhan/mukhiya, ek purush dharmik neta jo monks ko lead karta hai.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> The head of a monastery.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi math (monastery) ke pradhan ko — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Abbot ne aane wale monks ka monastery mein garmjoshi se swagat kiya.\" data-example=\"The abbot welcomed the visiting monks into the monastery.\">Abbot</span> was a quiet man named Brother Elias, who had governed the order since before most townspeople were born."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 2",
      "text": "Lately, something strange had happened — the usual noise of the town had begun to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abate\" data-syno=\"subside, decrease, wane\" data-anto=\"intensify, increase\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"kam hona ya ghatna\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abate ka matlab hai kam hona ya ghatna — intensity ya severity ka dheere-dheere kam hona.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Something gradually becoming less intense, like a storm or pain.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab koi cheez (jaise toofan, dard ya gussa) dheere-dheere kam hone lagti hai — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Shaam tak toofan abate ho gaya aur jahaaz safely harbour se nikal paaye.\" data-example=\"The storm began to abate by evening, letting ships leave harbor safely.\">Abate</span>. Even the old <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abattoir\" data-syno=\"slaughterhouse\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"kasaikhana\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abattoir ka matlab hai kasaikhana — jahan jaanwaron ko maans ke liye kaata jaata hai.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> A place where animals are slaughtered for food.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Wo jagah jahan jaanwaron ko khane ke liye maara jaata hai — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Naye abattoir mein hygiene ke sakht niyam follow kiye jaate hain.\" data-example=\"The new abattoir on the outskirts follows strict hygiene regulations.\">Abattoir</span> near the market had gone quiet, its workers sent home without explanation. Journalist Meera called it a genuine <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Aberration\" data-syno=\"anomaly, deviation, irregularity\" data-anto=\"normalcy, regularity\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"asaamanyata\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Aberration ka matlab hai asaamanyata — sahi ya samanya raaste se hatna ya bhatakna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Deviation from the right course.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab sahi raaste se bhatak jaana — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Uska itna gussa hona ek aberration tha, warna woh hamesha shaant rehta hai.\" data-example=\"His sudden anger was an aberration from his usually calm nature.\">Aberration</span> and decided to find out more."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 3",
      "text": "She learned that Brother Elias performed his <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Ablution\" data-syno=\"washing, cleansing\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"sharir ko dhona\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Ablution ka matlab hai sharir ko dhona, aksar dharmik rituals se pehle.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> The act of washing oneself.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab khud ko nahane/dhone ki kriya ko — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Woh roz prayer se pehle apni morning ablution zaroor karta tha.\" data-example=\"He performed his morning ablutions before the prayer.\">Ablution</span> at dawn each day by the river — a ritual he had never once skipped in forty years. This time, he had missed three mornings in a row."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 4",
      "text": "The monastery's official records used a strange <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abbreviation\" data-syno=\"shortening, acronym\" data-anto=\"expansion\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"sankshipt roop\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abbreviation ka matlab hai sankshipt roop — poore shabd ko chhota karke likhna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Shortening a word to represent the whole.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi shabd ko sankshipt roop mein likhna, jisse poore shabd ka pata chale — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> \"Dr.\" Doctor ka common abbreviation hai jo har jagah use hota hai.\" data-example=\"Dr. is the abbreviation for Doctor.\">Abbreviation</span> for donations that no one in town could explain. To Meera, chasing this thread felt almost <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Absurd\" data-syno=\"ridiculous, ludicrous, preposterous\" data-anto=\"sensible, reasonable\" data-pos=\"Adj.\" data-hindi=\"bahut hi anuchit ya hasyaaspad jo\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Absurd ka matlab hai bahut hi anuchit ya hasyaaspad jo logic se pare ho.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Something wildly unreasonable, illogical, or ridiculous.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Koi baat jo bilkul anuchit, tarkaheen ya hasyaaspad ho — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Overnight project poora karne ki umeed karna bilkul absurd tha.\" data-example=\"It was absurd to expect him to finish the project overnight.\">Absurd</span>, but she pressed on anyway."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 5",
      "text": "Rumours spread that the Abbot planned to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abdicate\" data-syno=\"resign, renounce, relinquish\" data-anto=\"assume, claim\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"apna pad ya adhikar chhod dena\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abdicate ka matlab hai apna pad ya adhikar chhod dena, khaaskar raja-rani ke context mein.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Giving up one's authority or throne.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab apne pad ya adhikar ko chhod dena — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Raja ne apne bete ke haq mein gaddi abdicate karne ka faisla liya.\" data-example=\"The king decided to abdicate the throne in favor of his son.\">Abdicate</span> his position. When the <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abdication\" data-syno=\"resignation, renunciation\" data-anto=\"assumption\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"gaddi tyaag\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abdication ka matlab hai gaddi tyaag — pad ya adhikar ko aupcharik roop se chhodna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> The act of giving up the throne.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab raja-gaddi ko tyaag dene ki kriya ko — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Uski achanak abdication ne poore desh ko chaunka diya tha.\" data-example=\"His abdication shocked the entire nation.\">Abdication</span> was finally announced, the whole town gathered outside the gates, stunned that their quiet leader was stepping down."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 6",
      "text": "Brother Elias explained that he wished to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abnegate\" data-syno=\"renounce, forgo, relinquish\" data-anto=\"indulge, claim\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"tyaagna\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abnegate ka matlab hai tyaagna — khud ko kisi sukh ya adhikar se vanchit karna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Refusing or denying oneself something.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab khud kisi cheez se inkaar karna ya khud ko us se vanchit karna — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Family ke liye usne apna personal comfort abnegate karne ka faisla liya.\" data-example=\"She chose to abnegate personal comfort for her family's sake.\">Abnegate</span> the comforts of his position. He also wanted the monastery to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abolish\" data-syno=\"eliminate, abrogate, eradicate\" data-anto=\"establish, institute\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"kisi rivaaz ya nirman ko poori\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abolish ka matlab hai kisi rivaaz ya nirman ko poori tarah samapt karna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Formally ending a system, practice, or institution.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi niyam, pratha ya sansthan ko aupcharik roop se samapt karna — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Sarkar ne purana aur outdated tax law abolish karne ka vote diya.\" data-example=\"The government voted to abolish the outdated tax law.\">Abolish</span> an old rule that barred local <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Aboriginal\" data-syno=\"indigenous, native\" data-anto=\"foreign, alien\" data-pos=\"Adj.\" data-hindi=\"kisi desh ka sabse purana mool\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Aboriginal ka matlab hai kisi desh ka sabse purana mool nivasi, jo colonists se pehle se wahan tha.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Existing in a land from the earliest times before colonists arrived.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi desh mein sabse pehle se ya colonist ke aane se pehle se rehne wale ko — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Australia mein Aboriginal tribes hazaron saalon se rehte aa rahe hain.\" data-example=\"Aboriginal tribes have lived in Australia for thousands of years.\">Aboriginal</span> families from worshipping there."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 7",
      "text": "For generations, the <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Aborigines\" data-syno=\"natives, indigenes\" data-anto=\"settlers, colonists\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"kisi desh ke mool nivasi/native log\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Aborigines ka matlab hai kisi desh ke mool nivasi/native log.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> The original inhabitants/natives of a country.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi desh ke mool nivasiyon ko — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Us ilaake ke aborigines ne apni traditions ko sadiyon tak zinda rakha.\" data-example=\"The aborigines of the region maintained their traditions for centuries.\">Aborigines</span> of the valley had been quietly turned away at the gate. Elias called it the monastery's greatest shame, one he intended to correct before he left."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 8",
      "text": "Meera wanted to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abridge\" data-syno=\"shorten, condense, curtail\" data-anto=\"expand, lengthen\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"sankshipt karna\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abridge ka matlab hai sankshipt karna — likhi hui cheez ko chota karna par arth na khona.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Shortening a piece of writing without losing its sense.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi likhit cheez ko uska arth khoye bina chota karna — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Publisher ne young readers ke liye novel ko abridge karne ka decision liya.\" data-example=\"The publisher decided to abridge the novel for younger readers.\">Abridge</span> her long investigation into something readable — a short <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abridgement\" data-syno=\"summary, condensation\" data-anto=\"expansion\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"sankshipt sanskaran\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abridgement ka matlab hai sankshipt sanskaran — kisi badi book ya rachna ka chota roop.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> A shortened version of a larger work.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi badi rachna ka sankshipt sanskaran (version) ko — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Maine original padhne se pehle classic novel ka abridgement padh liya tha.\" data-example=\"I read the abridgement of the classic novel before the original.\">Abridgement</span> the town could actually finish reading before the Sunday paper went to print."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 9",
      "text": "Her editor wanted to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abrogate\" data-syno=\"annul, repeal, revoke\" data-anto=\"enact, establish\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"aupcharik roop se kisi kanoon ya\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abrogate ka matlab hai aupcharik roop se kisi kanoon ya samjhauta ko rad karna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Canceling or doing away with a law or agreement.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi kanoon ya samjhauta ko rad ya samapt karna — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Nayi government ne purani trade treaty ko abrogate karne ka faisla liya.\" data-example=\"The new government decided to abrogate the old trade treaty.\">Abrogate</span> the whole story, fearing backlash from old donors. Meera refused, worried the truth might simply <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Abscond\" data-syno=\"flee, escape, decamp\" data-anto=\"remain, surrender\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"farar hona\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Abscond ka matlab hai farar hona — gupt roop se aur achanak bhaag jaana, aksar paise ya zimmedari se bachne ke liye.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Going away suddenly and secretly to escape from somewhere.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab kahin se bhaag jaana taaki pakda na jaaye — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Cashier company ka fund lekar abscond ho gaya, wapas nahi aaya.\" data-example=\"The cashier absconded with the company's funds.\">Abscond</span> into silence forever."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 10",
      "text": "When she finally published it, the town reacted with something closer to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Absolution\" data-syno=\"forgiveness, pardon\" data-anto=\"condemnation, blame\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"paap-mukti ya kshama\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Absolution ka matlab hai paap-mukti ya kshama, aksar dharmik context mein use hota hai.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> The formal forgiveness of a person's sins.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi vyakti ke paapon ki aupcharik kshama ko — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Confession ke baad priest ne usse absolution de di.\" data-example=\"The priest granted him absolution after confession.\">Absolution</span> — as if a long-held guilt had finally been allowed to surface and heal."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 11",
      "text": "The mayor's office moved to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accelerate\" data-syno=\"speed up, hasten, expedite\" data-anto=\"decelerate, slow down\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"gati badhana\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Accelerate ka matlab hai gati badhana — speed ko tez karna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Increasing the speed.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab gati ko badhana — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Highway pe safely merge karne ke liye driver ko accelerate karna pada.\" data-example=\"The driver had to accelerate to merge onto the highway safely.\">Accelerate</span> the reforms Brother Elias had proposed, and within a month the monastery gave Meera a rare public <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accolade\" data-syno=\"honour, praise, tribute\" data-anto=\"criticism, censure\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"puraskar ya samman jo achievement ke\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Accolade ka matlab hai puraskar ya samman jo achievement ke liye diya jaata hai.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> An award, honour, or laudatory notice.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Koi puraskar, samman ya prashansa jo kisi achchhe kaam ke liye di jaaye — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Medicine mein apni research ke liye usse ek accolade mila.\" data-example=\"She received an accolade for her outstanding research in medicine.\">Accolade</span> for her reporting."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 12",
      "text": "Not everyone was pleased. A former <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accomplice\" data-syno=\"collaborator, partner-in-crime\" data-anto=\"opponent, rival\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"sah-apradhi\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Accomplice ka matlab hai sah-apradhi — wo vyakti jo kisi crime mein saath deta hai.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> A person who helps another commit a crime.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Wo vyakti jo kisi aur ko apraadh karne mein madad karta hai — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Police ne chor ke saath uske accomplice ko bhi arrest kar liya.\" data-example=\"Police arrested both the thief and his accomplice.\">Accomplice</span> of the old donor group tried to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accord\" data-syno=\"agreement, harmony, concur\" data-anto=\"discord, disagree\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"anuroop hona\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Accord ka matlab hai anuroop hona — kisi baat ya niyam se mel khana.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Being harmonious or consistent with something.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi cheez ke anuroop ya samanjasya mein hona — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Uske actions uski kahi hui baaton se bilkul accord nahi karte the.\" data-example=\"His actions accord with the company's core values.\">Accord</span> his own version of events, hoping to twist the story back in his favour."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 13",
      "text": "A retired <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Accountant\" data-syno=\"auditor, bookkeeper\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"munim/lekhpal\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Accountant ka matlab hai munim/lekhpal — jo hisaab-kitaab rakhne ka kaam karta hai.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> A person whose profession is to keep accounts.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab jiska pesha accounts (hisaab-kitaab) rakhna hai — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Accountant ne saal ke ant mein har invoice carefully check ki.\" data-example=\"The accountant reviewed the company's financial statements carefully.\">Accountant</span> who had once managed the monastery's books came forward too, offering blunt, <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acerbic\" data-syno=\"sharp, biting, caustic\" data-anto=\"gentle, mild\" data-pos=\"Adj.\" data-hindi=\"kadwa swabhaav\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Acerbic ka matlab hai kadwa swabhaav — teekhi aur kathor baat-cheet ya temperament.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Being sharp, bitter, or harsh in temper or language.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab swabhaav, bhasha aadi mein teekha, kadwa ya kathor hona — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Critic apne acerbic reviews ke liye jaana jaata tha, kisi ko nahi bakhsta.\" data-example=\"Her acerbic comments often hurt her colleagues' feelings.\">Acerbic</span> testimony about decades of quiet discrimination hidden in the ledgers."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 14",
      "text": "The town hall meeting where he spoke had famously poor <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acoustics\" data-syno=\"sound-quality\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"dhwani-vigyan\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Acoustics ka matlab hai dhwani-vigyan — sound aur uske behavior ka scientific study.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> The scientific study of sound.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab dhwani ka vaigyanik adhyayan — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Hall ki acoustics itni acchi thi ki har awaaz clearly sunai deti thi.\" data-example=\"The hall's acoustics made every word clearly audible.\">Acoustics</span> — but everyone in the room understood every word. A local court was even asked to formally <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acquit\" data-syno=\"exonerate, absolve, clear\" data-anto=\"convict, condemn\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"bari karna\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Acquit ka matlab hai bari karna — court dwara kisi vyakti ko nirdosh ghoshit karna.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Officially declaring someone not guilty in court.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab court mein aupcharik roop se yeh kehna ki vyakti doshi nahi hai — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Jury ne sirf do ghante mein defendant ko acquit kar diya, evidence hi nahi tha.\" data-example=\"The jury decided to acquit the defendant due to lack of evidence.\">Acquit</span> the Aboriginal families of old, false accusations."
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 15",
      "text": "On the day the gates finally opened to everyone, a travelling <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acrobat\" data-syno=\"gymnast, tumbler\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"hawai/risky karatab dikhane wala kalakaar\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Acrobat ka matlab hai hawai/risky karatab dikhane wala kalakaar.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> An entertainer who performs difficult physical feats.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Wo manoranjak jo mushkil sharirik karatab karta hai — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Circus ka acrobat trapeze act ekdum stunning tarike se perform karta tha.\" data-example=\"The circus acrobat performed a stunning trapeze act.\">Acrobat</span> performed in the courtyard for the children of the valley. Someone in the crowd joked that the whole event deserved its own <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acronym\" data-syno=\"abbreviation, initialism\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"shabdon ke pehle akshar se bana\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Acronym ka matlab hai shabdon ke pehle akshar se bana sankshipt shabd.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> An abbreviation formed from initial letters and pronounced as a word.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab dusre shabdon ke pehle akshar se bana aur shabd ki tarah uchcharit — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> NASA National Aeronautics and Space Administration ka acronym hai.\" data-example=\"NASA is an acronym for National Aeronautics and Space Administration.\">Acronym</span> — \"T.O.O.\" for \"The Opening of the Old gates.\""
    },
    {
      "n": "¶ 16",
      "text": "Meera, who had always had a mild <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Acrophobia\" data-syno=\"fear of heights\" data-anto=\"\" data-pos=\"N.\" data-hindi=\"uchaai se ghabrahat ya dar\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Acrophobia ka matlab hai uchaai se ghabrahat ya dar.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> The fear of great heights.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Jab uchaai ka dar — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Uski acrophobia ki wajah se woh cliff ke edge ke paas khada hi nahi hua.\" data-example=\"Due to his acrophobia, he refused to stand near the edge of the cliff.\">Acrophobia</span>, still climbed to the highest step of the bell tower that evening to watch the celebration below. It felt like the right way to <span class=\"vw\" data-word=\"Act\" data-syno=\"perform, behave, do\" data-anto=\"abstain, refrain\" data-pos=\"V.\" data-hindi=\"kuch karna ya kisi tarah vyavhar\" data-meaning=\"🧠 <b>Matlab:</b> Act ka matlab hai kuch karna ya kisi tarah vyavhar karna, jaise kisi natak mein role nibhana.<br>📖 <b>English:</b> Behaving in a particular way or performing a part in a play.<br>📍 <b>Kab use karein:</b> Kisi tarah se vyavhar karna ya kisi role ko nibhana — tab yeh shabd bolte hain.<br>💬 <b>Example (Hinglish):</b> Fire alarm baja toh usse turant act karna pada.\" data-example=\"She had to act quickly when the fire alarm rang.\">Act</span> on a story finally told in full."
    }
  ]
}
